Ms. Han, you won't not help me, will you?

50
00:02:30,050 --> 00:02:31,240
I've already talked to them

51
00:02:31,290 --> 00:02:32,730
what I should say.

52
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:35,050
If you still need me to persuade them,

53
00:02:35,410 --> 00:02:37,130
I always have time.

54
00:02:37,890 --> 00:02:38,960
But as the old saying goes,

55
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,920
whoever started the trouble should end it.

56
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:42,960
They are your guardians.

57
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,570
If you can't understand this,

58
00:02:45,570 --> 00:02:47,170
my help will be useless.

59
00:02:47,170 --> 00:02:48,010
Do you know?

60
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:50,640
I know.

61
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:53,340
(Songbei Province Ice Sports Base)

62
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,310
Hello, Mr. Nie, Mrs. Nie.

63
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,850
I am Lin Ge, Nie Chi's teammate.

64
00:02:56,330 --> 00:02:57,170
- Hello.
- Hello.

65
00:02:57,450 --> 00:02:58,680
You invited us here, right?

66
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:00,800
Where is Nie Chi?

67
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,240
Didn't you say to take us to see him?

68
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,520
Mr. Nie, Mrs. Nie,

69
00:03:03,530 --> 00:03:05,410
I'm going to take you to see him.

70
00:03:05,410 --> 00:03:06,480
- Go with me.
- Ok.

71
00:03:08,170 --> 00:03:09,010
Let's go.

72
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:14,420
(Everything about Nie Chi)

73
00:03:15,130 --> 00:03:16,610
(Genius boy Nie Chi)
His name is Nie Chi.

74
00:03:17,010 --> 00:03:17,920
At the age

75
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,920
when peers would cry over scraped knees,

76
00:03:20,010 --> 00:03:21,480
he had already left his parents

77
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,010
and entered the sports school alone

78
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:24,520
to undergo rigorous training.

79
00:03:25,140 --> 00:03:26,460
(Gifted in youth)
In adolescence

80
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,480
that is troublesome for parents,

81
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,200
he went through a brutal selection process

82
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,360
to join the provincial team

83
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,760
and spent all the time

84
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,200
on training.

85
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,890
He used up all his strength

86
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:37,610
in every competition

87
00:03:37,610 --> 00:03:38,850
and fought until the end

88
00:03:39,170 --> 00:03:40,640
to win the national championship.

89
00:03:41,010 --> 00:03:42,570
He loves short track speed skating

90
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:45,290
(Champion)
and has devoted himself to it.

91
00:03:45,450 --> 00:03:46,640
The dream

92
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,730
of this talented young man

93
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:49,480
is to stand on the world stage,

94
00:03:49,650 --> 00:03:51,010
(We are the champions)
fight for the dream,

95
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,720
and bring glory to the country.

96
00:03:53,260 --> 00:03:54,680
(Gao Kai, a vibrant national athlete)

97
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,850
Mr. Nie, Mrs. Nie, please take a look.

98
00:03:56,050 --> 00:03:58,050
This is our senior Gao Kai.

99
00:03:58,050 --> 00:03:59,640
He is now the captain of the national team

100
00:03:59,890 --> 00:04:02,050
and also the world champion in the 500m.

101
00:04:02,050 --> 00:04:03,130
He is an athlete?

102
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:04,410
Yes.

103
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:06,850
I thought he is a celebrity.

104
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:10,610
I am Gao Kai,

105
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:13,450
the captain of the national team.

106
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,640
Although I am not a celebrity,

107
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:17,650
when it comes to contribution and value,

108
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,730
I don't lose to them.

109
00:04:19,610 --> 00:04:22,210
We bear the glory of the country on us.

110
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,680
Dad, Mom,

111
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,680
I am here to apologize to you all.

112
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,320
No matter what the reason is,

113
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,880
I did not keep my promise

114
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:31,290
to study abroad.

115
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:32,440
It is my fault.

116
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,970
I apologize to you.

117
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:35,610
I'm sorry.

118
00:04:36,690 --> 00:04:37,730
Mrs. Nie, you may not know yet,

119
00:04:37,730 --> 00:04:39,240
Gao Kai is optimistic about Nie Chi.

120
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,560
He believes Nie Chi will definitely make it.

121
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,440
After hearing you would take Nie Chi abroad

122
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,730
and let him give up,

123
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:47,290
he rushed back to persuade Nie Chi to stay.

124
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,560
I really love short track speed skating.

125
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,320
When I was a child,

126
00:04:51,530 --> 00:04:52,920
you have arranged everything for me.

127
00:04:53,530 --> 00:04:54,680
Only when I was on the ice,

128
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,320
I feel free

129
00:04:57,050 --> 00:04:59,530
and I feel that my life is under my control.

130
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,770
I like skating.

131
00:05:02,210 --> 00:05:03,880
Just like you love your own career.

132
00:05:05,050 --> 00:05:06,000
If one day someone

133
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,980
forcibly changes the path of your life,

134
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,920
what are you going to do?

135
00:05:11,730 --> 00:05:13,650
Nie Chi is a very,

136
00:05:13,650 --> 00:05:16,000
very good short track speed skater.

137
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,440
His future is quite bright.

138
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:19,970
If he gives up at this moment,

139
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,440
it would be really a pity.

140
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:25,120
Is Nie Chi

141
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,530
really as excellent as you say?

142
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:27,970
- Absolutely.
- Absolutely.

143
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,320
Nie, well...

144
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:32,880
I'm well-know for cherishing my body.

145
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,650
Because I want to keep going.

146
00:05:37,530 --> 00:05:38,730
I assure you

147
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,610
I will never get injured.

148
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,640
So,

149
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:44,970
do you want me to continue?

150
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:54,770
Son, what's your ultimate goal

151
00:05:55,410 --> 00:05:56,770
to choose the short track speed skating?

152
00:05:57,210 --> 00:05:58,320
I want to join the national team.

153
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,970
I want to become a world champion,

154
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,480
a top short track speed skater in the world.

155
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,090
Good boy!

156
00:06:05,770 --> 00:06:06,610
Ok.

157
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,480
Then let's make another agreement.

158
00:06:09,410 --> 00:06:11,880
If you can make it within a year,

159
00:06:12,610 --> 00:06:14,120
I will let you continue it.

160
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:15,730
If not,

161
00:06:16,090 --> 00:06:18,470
you will obediently study abroad.

162
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:21,580
I am reasonable, right?

163
00:06:22,290 --> 00:06:23,970
The logic is simple and direct.

164
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,320
But I promise you.

165
00:06:26,850 --> 00:06:28,880
Lin Ge, you are really a good girl.

166
00:06:28,970 --> 00:06:30,530
You are talkative.

167
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:33,070
And you understand Nie Chi well.

168
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,480
- What's your ranking?
- I like you.

169
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,880
First or second, I guess.

170
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,240
Really?

171
00:06:39,770 --> 00:06:41,480
Let's keep in touch more often.

172
00:06:42,050 --> 00:06:43,290
You need to report

173
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,090
every move of Nie Chi to me.

174
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,440
All right, Mrs. Nie.

175
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,520
Then I'm leaving.

176
00:06:48,780 --> 00:06:50,360
Please be safe on the road.

177
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,780
Goodbye.

178
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,290
Let's go.

179
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:03,770
It turns out

180
00:07:03,850 --> 00:07:05,650
communication is more effective, right?

181
00:07:05,970 --> 00:07:06,810
Yes, it is.

182
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,410
Sometimes I feel that

183
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,770
communication is just wasting energy.

184
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,800
Whether it is the matter with Huang Han

185
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,440
or the matter with my parents this time,

186
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,520
it's all the same.

187
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:16,090
Do you enjoy the sweet taste this time?

188
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,770
It's all thanks to your good presentation

189
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,840
and precise positioning.

190
00:07:20,410 --> 00:07:22,730
The plan is just right for my dad.

191
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,880
Luckily, you understand me.

192
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,170
Without you,

193
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,530
it seems to be the same as before.

194
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,320
You seem particularly eager about my matters.

195
00:07:32,730 --> 00:07:34,000
You really want to help ease

196
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,680
the relationship between my parents and me.

197
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,720
Yes.

198
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,080
Why?

199
00:07:38,650 --> 00:07:39,560
Because

200
00:07:41,210 --> 00:07:42,610
hating your own family

201
00:07:42,850 --> 00:07:44,050
is a painful thing.

202
00:07:44,610 --> 00:07:46,090
I don't want you and your parents

203
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,240
to take a step that is irreparable.

204
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,610
Do you know

205
00:07:49,610 --> 00:07:50,920
I'm quite envious of you?

206
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:53,800
I also want my family to watch me compete.

207
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,920
But all the people who loved me have left.

208
00:07:58,210 --> 00:07:59,150
Don't talk about it anymore.

209
00:07:59,970 --> 00:08:01,210
I almost forgot the important matter.

210
00:08:01,730 --> 00:08:02,680
What's the matter?

211
00:08:03,770 --> 00:08:05,050
The round-trip tickets for Gao Kai,

212
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,730
the hotel expenses he spent,

213
00:08:06,730 --> 00:08:09,050
including expenses for food and drinks.

214
00:08:09,530 --> 00:08:10,920
And also the money for the presentation.

215
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,560
When are you free to reimburse it?

216
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,290
Does the presentation also cost money?

217
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,350
Of course.

218
00:08:19,210 --> 00:08:20,610
Nie, let me tell you,

219
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,650
Lin Ge is truly a hero this time.

220
00:08:22,850 --> 00:08:24,120
She has been very busy,

221
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,740
making the presentation,

222
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,650
inviting Gao Kai,

223
00:08:27,850 --> 00:08:29,290
and planning all of this.

224
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,970
You should sincerely thank

225
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,440
me.

226
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:37,320
I pulled the curtains

227
00:08:37,410 --> 00:08:38,530
and turned on and off the lights.

228
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,080
I also turned pages.

229
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,770
How important my work is.

230
00:08:41,890 --> 00:08:42,920
Once I get stuck on my work,

231
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,530
then the whole process will be ruined.

232
00:08:45,650 --> 00:08:47,560
Anyway, don't think you can fool us

233
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:49,530
with such a meal.

234
00:08:49,530 --> 00:08:50,370
Fine.

235
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:51,920
I'll treat you both to a meal outside.

236
00:08:54,370 --> 00:08:56,490
But let me tell you honestly,

237
00:08:56,890 --> 00:08:57,800
you really need to hurry up.

238
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,410
You have already promised your parents

239
00:08:59,410 --> 00:09:01,050
that you must make it within a year.

240
00:09:01,290 --> 00:09:02,560
If you can't make it,

241
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:04,220
when your dad and mom come next time,

242
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:06,250
no matter how well we perform,

243
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:07,090
it's useless anyway.

244
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,800
The Starlight Cup is a common hurdle for us.

245
00:09:13,530 --> 00:09:15,530
Let me toast to Lin Ge first.

246
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,050
My work is very important.

247
00:09:19,130 --> 00:09:19,970
Together.

248
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:00,050
Zhu Zhu, you're still practicing so late.

249
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,840
Aren't you also here

250
00:10:06,050 --> 00:10:07,410
for extra practice at this late hour?

251
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,440
Is your leg injury healing up well?

252
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,800
It's almost healed.

253
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:17,800
That's fine.

254
00:10:18,050 --> 00:10:19,370
I'm going to practice on the machines.

255
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,440
All right, you go ahead.

256
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,040
Nie Chi.

257
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,770
45s.

258
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,250
My time is finally less than 45s.

259
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,840
- Really?
- Thank you so much.

260
00:10:44,530 --> 00:10:45,650
What are you thanking me for?

261
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,720
It's about making arcs when turning.

262
00:10:48,560 --> 00:10:50,630
How did you come up with it?

263
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:51,530
It's not me.

264
00:10:51,530 --> 00:10:52,920
As soon as I learned this during turns,

265
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:54,600
my speed really improved a lot.

266
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,680
If I practice this more,

267
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:58,490
my grades can continue to be improved.

268
00:10:59,250 --> 00:11:01,440
Because my legs hurt when turning.

269
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:04,720
Maybe the time for making an arc is too long.

270
00:11:05,170 --> 00:11:07,130
The longer it is, the slower the speed is.

271
00:11:07,290 --> 00:11:08,530
And the legs easily get sore.

272
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,920
So that's the reason.

273
00:11:21,490 --> 00:11:22,960
If you practice hard,

274
00:11:23,170 --> 00:11:24,130
there will be breakthroughs.

275
00:11:24,530 --> 00:11:25,530
I think so too.

276
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:26,920
Where's Fang Chao?

277
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,440
I want to tell him this good news.

278
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:31,050
Zhu Zhu, are you going back?

279
00:11:31,050 --> 00:11:32,290
I'll go with you.

